  "text": "Tissue cultures. The human diploid cell strain WI-38 [CITATION_1] and two hamster cell lines, BHK-21 clone 13 [CITATION_2] and Nil-2 cells (4), were propagated in 1-liter Blake bottles as described by Kaplan et al. (21) .",
